  "description": "A dramatic sunset over a body of water and distant mountains. The sky is ablaze with fiery orange and red hues, streaked with wispy, elongated clouds. These clouds radiate outwards from a central point near the horizon, creating a dynamic and almost painterly effect. The water reflects some of the sunset's colors, though it appears darker overall. Below, a silhouetted landscape of land and buildings is visible, suggesting a coastal city or town. The overall impression is one of grandeur and natural beauty.",
